#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:95
msgid ""
"A client's home is defined as the house, caravan, houseboat or other vehicle or structure that is their only or main residence. The references to caravan, houseboat or other vehicle include the land on which it is located or to which it is moored.\n"
"\n"
"Operators should interpret the definition as a client would only be in scope if they lived in the home in question. If someone lives or owns another property and the matter relates to a different proeperty to the one they live in then this would be out of scope.\n"
"\n"
"If the client is a co-owner of the property and they live in it as their only or main residence (as per the definition of 'home') then this would be in scope.\n"
"\n"
"Search guidance for 'timeline' to see the home repossession timeline.\n"
"\n"
"*FYI: Debt matters need to arise from an issue where the client owns their own home. Problems relating to homes that are rented or leased from another person fall within Housing.*"
msgstr ""
"Diffinnir cartref y cleient fel tŷ, carafan, cwch preswyl neu gerbyd neu strwythur arall os mai hwn yw ei unig neu ei brif fan preswylio. Pan gyfeirir at garafan, cwch preswyl neu gerbyd arall, mae'r tir lle mae wedi'i leoli neu ei glymu yn cael ei gynnwys hefyd. \n"
"\n"
"Dylai gweithredwyr ddehongli'r diffiniad y byddai cleient ond yn y cwmpas os ydynt yn byw yn y cartref dan sylw. Os yw rhywun yn byw neu'n berchen ar eiddo arall a bod y mater yn berthnasol i eiddo sy'n wahanol i'r un y maent yn byw ynddo, yna byddai hyn allan o'r cwmpas.\n"
"\n"
"Os yw'r cleient yn gyd-berchennog o'r eiddo ac yn byw ynddo fel ei unig neu ei brif fan preswyl (dan y diffiniad o 'cartref') yna byddai hyn yn y cwmpas.\n"
"\n"
"Chwiliwch am ganllaw 'llinell amser' i weld llinell amser ailfeddiannu cartref.\n"
"\n"
"*Er gwybodaeth: Mae problemau dyled angen codi o faterion lle mae'r cleient yn berchen ar ei gartref ei hun. Mae problemau yn berthnasol i gartrefi sy'n cael eu rhentu neu ar brydles gan unigolyn arall yn dod o dan 'Tai'.*"

