#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1134
msgid ""
"This refers to discrimination against people of a:\n"
"* particular age (eg 19-year-olds), or\n"
"* range of ages (eg 60 to 80-year-olds)"
msgstr ""
"Mae hyn yn cyfeirio at wahaniaethu yn erbyn pobl:\n"
"* o oedran penodol (e.e. pobl 19 oed), neu \n"
"* ystod oedran (e.e. pobl 60 i 80 oed)"

