msgstr "Cyflawni gweithred gyhoeddus (e.e. heddwas yn cyflawni chwiliad) "

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1237
msgid "Being married or in a civil partnership"
msgstr "Bod yn briod neu mewn partneriaeth sifil"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1240
msgid "This refers to people who are married or in a civil partnership, including same sex couples."
msgstr "Mae hyn yn cyfeirio at bobl sydd wedi priodi neu mewn partneriaeth sifil, gan gynnwys cyplau o'r un rhyw."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1277
msgid "Indirect discrimination"
msgstr "Gwahaniaethu anuniongyrchol"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1280
msgid "The client thinks that new ways of doing things have put them at a disadvantage compared to someone else because of a protected characteristic (eg an employer states that employees cannot have dreadlocks or a pub refuses access to people with hats. This puts employees or patrons of a certain religion at a disadvantage when compared to others.)"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient yn credu bod y ffyrdd newydd o wneud pethau wedi ei roi dan anfantais o'i gymharu â rhywun arall oherwydd nodweddion gwarchodedig (e.e. cyflogwr yn nodi na all gweithwyr gael gwallt rhaffog neu dafarn yn gwrthod mynediad i bobl sydd yn gwisgo hetiau. Mae hyn yn rhoi gweithwyr neu noddwyr crefyddau penodedig dan anfantais o'i gymharu ag eraill.)"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1290
msgid "Something happened to make the client feel that they were in an environment that was intimidating, hostile, degrading, humiliating or offensive or that violated their dignity."
msgstr "Digwyddodd rhywbeth i'r cleient i wneud iddynt deimlo eu bod mewn amgylchedd a oedd yn fygythiol, gelyniaethus, diraddiol, darostyngol neu ymosodol neu wedi bradychu eu hurddas."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1297
msgid "Victimisation due to a discrimination claim"
msgstr "Cael eich erlid oherwydd honiad ynghylch gwahaniaethu"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1300
msgid "The client thinks that they have been treated worse, or disadvantaged in some way, because they have brought a claim of discrimination, given evidence or information in relation to someone else’s claim of discrimination, made a complaint of discrimination, or been suspected of doing one of these things. For example, an employee is dismissed after making a discrimination claim."
msgstr "Mae'r cleient yn credu ei fod wedi cael ei drin yn waeth, neu o dan anfantais mewn rhyw ffordd, oherwydd eu bod wedi gwneud hawliad am wahaniaethu, rhoi tystiolaeth neu wybodaeth mewn perthynas â hawliad rhywun arall am wahaniaethu, wedi gwneud cwyn am wahaniaethu, neu wedi cael ei ddrwgdybio o wneud un o'r rhain. Er enghraifft, gweithiwr yn cael ei ddiswyddo ar ôl gwneud hawliad am wahaniaethu.  "

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1307
msgid "Special educational needs (SEN) in a child or young person under 25 - client could be the parent or the child or young person"
msgstr "Anghenion addysgol arbennig (SEN) mewn plentyn neu berson ifanc dan 25 - gallai'r cleient fod yn rhiant, neu'r plentyn neu berson ifanc ei hun "

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1323
msgid "Advised to bring judicial review proceedings in an education matter"
msgstr "Cynghorwyd i ddechrau achos am adolygiad barnwrol mewn perthynas â mater addysg"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1339
msgid "Discrimination may have occurred due to the child or young person’s SEN or other protected characteristic (eg a school excludes a disabled child from a school trip, a student is being bullied because they're gay but the school is taking no action)"
msgstr "Gallai'r gwahaniaethu fod wedi digwydd oherwydd SEN y plentyn neu'r unigolyn ifanc neu nodwedd gwarchodedig arall (e.e. ysgol yn gwahardd plentyn anabl rhag mynd ar drip ysgol, myfyriwr yn cael ei fwlio oherwydd ei fod yn hoyw ond nid yw'r ysgol yn gwneud rhywbeth)"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1342
msgid "Search guidance for 'discrimination education' for more information and a list of questions to ask."
msgstr "Chwiliwch am 'addysg ar wahaniaethu' yn y canllaw i gael rhagor o wybodaeth a rhestr o gwestiynau i'w gofyn."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1346
msgid "The client's problem is about admissions, exclusions, other disciplinary procedures, school trips, bullying, any problems at school caused by a child’s disability or any other similar situation"
msgstr "Mae problem y cleient yn ymwneud ag addefiadau, gwaharddiadau, gweithdrefnau disgyblu eraill, tripiau ysgol, bwlio, unrhyw broblemau yn yr ysgol a achoswyd gan anabledd plentyn neu sefyllfa arall debyg"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1353
msgid "Any other education problem"
msgstr "Unrhyw broblem arall yn ymwneud ag addysg"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1358
msgid "The client is a teacher or employee of the local authority"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient yn athro neu'n gyflogai i'r awdurdod lleol"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1374
msgid "The client is calling for general advice, not about a legal issue specific to them (eg they want to know if a school can stop them removing their child, as opposed to calling after the school has taken action against them for removing their child)"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient yn ffonio am gyngor cyffredinol, nid ynghylch mater cyfreithiol sy'n benodol iddynt hwy (e.e. maent eisiau gwybod os gall ysgol eu stopio rhag symud eu plentyn, yn hytrach na ffonio ar ôl i'r ysgol weithredu yn eu herbyn am symud eu plentyn)"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1392
msgid ""
"The welfare benefits category of law covers advice on:\n"
"\n"
"* entitlement to benefits and help when benefits are refused\n"
"* benefit appeals and tribunals\n"
"* problems with housing, welfare and disability benefits and tax credits\n"
"* advice on changes in circumstances that would affect benefits or tax credits\n"
"\n"
"The client's problem will be in scope for legal aid if:\n"
"\n"
"* they want to appeal a benefits decision on a point of law in the Upper Tribunal, Court of Appeal or Supreme Court\n"
"* a first-tier tribunal has refused them permission to appeal a benefits decision in the Upper Tribunal, and they want advice about how to appeal this decision\n"
"\n"
"All other benefit problems are out of scope."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r categori cyfraith budd-daliadau lles yn cynnwys cyngor am:\n"
"\n"
"* hawl i gael budd-daliadau a chymorth pan wrthodir budd-daliadau\n"
"* apeliadau i fudd-daliadau a thribiwnlysoedd\n"
"* problemau gyda budd-daliadau tai, lles ac anabledd a chredyd treth\n"
"\n"
"Bydd problem y cleient o fewn cwmpas ar gyfer cymorth cyfreithiol os:\n"
"\n"
"* ydynt eisiau apelio penderfyniad budd-daliadau ar bwynt cyfreithiol yn yr Uwch Dribiwnlys, y Llys Apêl neu'r Goruchaf Lys\n"
"* mae tribiwnlys haen gyntaf wedi gwrthod caniatâd i apelio penderfyniad budd-daliadau yn yr Uwch Dribiwnlys, ac maent eisiau cyngor am sut i apelio'r penderfyniad hwn\n"
"\n"
"Mae pob problem arall y tu allan i'r cwmpas."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1408
msgid "The client wants to appeal their benefits decision on a point of law in the Upper Tribunal, Court of Appeal or Supreme Court. (Or a first-tier tribunal has refused the client permission to appeal their benefits decision in the Upper Tribunal and they want advice about how to appeal this decision.)"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient eisiau apelio yn erbyn penderfyniad ynghlych eu budd-daliadau ar bwynt cyfreithiol yn yr Uwch Dribiwnlys, y Llys Apêl neu'r Goruchaf Lys. (Neu mae tribiwnlys haen gyntaf wedi gwrthod caniatâd i'r cleient apelio yn erbyn penderfyniad a wnaed ynghlych eu budd-daliadau yn yr Uwch Dribiwnlys, ac maent eisiau cyngor ar sut i apelio yn erbyn y penderfyniad hwn.)"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1442
msgid ""
"The employment category covers advice on\n"
"\n"
"* redundancies, dismissals and disciplinaries\n"
"* contracts, workers' rights and working hours\n"
"* rights at work including health &amp; safety and accidents at work\n"
"* employment status\n"
"* holidays, time off, sick leave, maternity &amp; paternity leave and other absence\n"
"* pay, tax and the National Minimum Wage."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r categori cyflogaeth yn cynnwys cyngor am\n"
"\n"
"* golli swydd, diswyddiadau a disgyblu\n"
"* cytundebau, hawliau gweithwyr ac oriau gwaith\n"
"* hawliau yn y gwaith gan gynnwys iechyd &amp; diogelwch a damweiniau yn y gwaith\n"
"* statws cyflogaeth\n"
"* gwyliau, amser i ffwrdd, absenoldeb salwch, mamolaeth &amp; absenoldeb tadolaeth ac absenoldebau eraill\n"
"* tâl, treth ac Isafswm Cyflog Cenedlaethol."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1453
msgid "The client may have been discriminated against (eg employer not making reasonable adjustments for a disability)"
msgstr "Mae'n bosib bod y cleient wedi profi gwahaniaethu (e.e. nid oedd cyflogwr yn gwneud addasiadau rhesymol ar gyfer anabledd)"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1456
msgid ""
"More examples of discrimination issues include issues around:\n"
"\n"
"* equal pay\n"
"* being treated worse due to pregnancy or maternity leave\n"
"* sexual harassment in the workplace\n"
"* being victimised due to having made a claim of discrimination in the workplace"
msgstr ""
"Rhagor o enghreifftiau o faterion gwahaniaethu yn cynnwys materion am:\n"
"\n"
"* dâl cyfartal\n"
"* cael eu trin yn waeth oherwydd beichiogrwydd neu gyfnod mamolaeth\n"
"* aflonyddu rhywiol yn y gweithle\n"
"* cael cam oherwydd eu bod wedi honni bod gwahaniaethu wedi digwydd yn y gweithle"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1465
msgid "Discrimination does not apply (Confirm no other matters such as homelessness arise as a result of employment issue)"
msgstr "Nid yw gwahaniaethu yn berthnasol (Cadarnhau nad oes materion eraill megis digartrefedd yn codi o ganlyniad i broblem cyflogaeth) "

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1480
msgid "Consumer"
msgstr "Defnyddiwr"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1483
msgid "The key thing to determine in this category is whether the client has been discriminated against. Discrimination cases will be in scope. All other consumer cases will be out of scope."
msgstr "Y peth allweddol i benderfynu yn ei gylch yn y categori hwn yw pa un ai a brofodd y cleient wahaniaethu ai peidio. Bydd achosion gwahaniaethu o fewn y cwmpas. Bydd holl achosion eraill yn ymwneud â defnyddwyr y tu allan i'r cwmpas."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1487
msgid "The client may have been discriminated against"
msgstr "Mae'n bosib bod y cleient wedi profi gwahaniaethu"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1492
#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1520
#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1649
#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1671
msgid "Discrimination does not apply"
msgstr "Nid yw gwahaniaethu yn berhtnasol"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1507
msgid "Claims against public authorities"
msgstr "Camau yn erbyn yr heddlu"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1510
msgid "The key thing to determine in claims against public authorities is whether the client has been discriminated against. If the client says they have been discriminated against, or if you pick up that they have been discriminated against from what they say, select 'The client has been discriminated against' on the next screen to proceed to the discrimination flow."
msgstr "Y peth allweddol i benderfynu yn ei gylch o ran camau yn erbyn yr heddlu yw pa un ai a brofodd y cleient wahaniaethu. Os yw'r cleient yn dweud ei fod wedi profi gwahaniaethu, neu eich bod yn sylweddoli eu bod wedi profi gwahaniaethu o'r hyn y maent yn ei ddweud, dewiswch 'Mae'r cleient wedi profi gwahaniaethu' ar y sgrin nesaf i barhau i'r llif gwahaniaethu."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1514
msgid "The client has been discriminated against (eg a police officer used racially abusive language when making an arrest)"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient wedi profi gwahaniaethu (h.y. heddwas wedi defnyddio iaith ddifrïol ar sail hil wrth arestio)"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1535
msgid "Crime"
msgstr "Trosedd"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1554
msgid ""
"Signpost clinical negligence cases to face-to-face providers in the client's area.\n"
"Generally, only cases that relate to infants with a brain injury are in scope for legal aid but it's possible that other cases may qualify for exceptional case funding."
msgstr ""
"Cyfeirio achosion esgeuluster clinigol i ddarparwyr wyneb yn wyneb yn ardal y cleient.\n"
"Yn gyffredinol, dim ond achosion sy'n berthnasol i blant bach ag anaf i'r ymenydd sydd o fewn cwmpas am gymorth cyfreithiol, ond mae'n bosibl y gall achosion eraill fod yn gymwys am gyllid i achosion arbennig."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1575
msgid "Any other matter"
msgstr "Unrhyw fater arall"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1590
msgid "The client is losing their home due to the Border Force refusing to support them or withdrawing their support"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient yn colli eu cartref oherwydd bod Llu'r Ffiniau yn gwrthod eu cefnogi neu yn tynnu eu cefnogaeth yn ôl"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1625
msgid "The key thing to determine in this category is whether the client has been discriminated against. Discrimination cases will be in scope. All other personal injury cases will be out of scope."
msgstr "Y peth allweddol yn y categori hwn yw pa un ai a brofodd y cleient wahaniaethu ai peidio. Bydd achosion o wahaniaethu o fewn y cwmpas. Bydd yr holl achosion anaf personol eraill y tu allan i'r cwmpas."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1639
#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1665
msgid "The client has been discriminated against"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient wedi profi gwahaniaethu"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1677
msgid "Client in rented accomodation"
